{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/CallToActionWishlist.gif?t=1728565767\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/DiceGambit_Title_TheFirstAct.png?t=1728565767\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Steam_Video_Header_Gif_Updated.gif?t=1728565767\" /><strong>The city of Neo-Talis is under threat as chromatic monsters have swarmed the Adicia power plant! Lead your own noble family of inquisitors as they cleanse the city, grow in power and make friends with eccentric nobles to - hopefully - save the city from disaster. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This demo covers the first act of Dice Gambit. By playing this and giving feedback you will help shape the future of the game! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Steam_Video_Turnbased_Gif_02.gif?t=1728565767\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate the battlefield by rolling dice and use them to control your knights in combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine dice to unleash your characters\u2019 powerful abilities and decimate your foes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reroll specific dice to be the master of your own fate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt to the roll of the dice to optimise your turn and achieve victory</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Steam_Video_customization_Gif_02.gif?t=1728565767\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock over 100 abilities and passives that completely change how your characters play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attend the Academy and pick amongst different classes each with unique mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shape your characters by freely mixing skills from the different classes however you like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break the game by discovering and creating over the top builds and synergies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Stecchi_SteamVideo_Updated_Small_03.gif?t=1728565767\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn favour with the extravagant elite of Neo-Talis and forge bonds to discover their secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your newfound allies' influence to open doors and unlock powerful skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Define your role in Neo-Talis by carefully considering which opportunities to pursue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who will be your allies as you rise up to save the city?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Steamvideo_family_Gif_02.gif?t=1728565767\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shape each playthrough to your liking, with the ability to make it extremely difficult - or wacky</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the mechanics of the game by finding different passives, abilities and the synergies between them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your family to make it truly your own</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give feedback to help us shape the game for the final release!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753240/extras/Steam_DiscordBanner.png?t=1728565767\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset